WHEELS VERSION 1.2.0 PREVIEW 1 11/18/2012

Model Enhancements
==================
* Allow for self joining tables in associations - #293 [James Gibson]
* Added "joinKey" on belongsTo(), hasOne() and hasMany() which allows you to specify a column to join to on the opposite side of the relationship from the "foreignKey" - [James Gibson]
* Added the ability to multijoin models - [Tony Petruzzi]
* Support for tableless models - [Tony Petruzzi]
* Add findFirst, findLast, findAllKeys, findOneOrCreateBy, findOrCreateBy - #745 [Mike Henke, Per Djurner, Tony Petruzzi]
* Enables use of UTC for wheels timestamps [Andy Bellenie]
* Allow models to be created when with no properties - #84 [rshakespear, Tony Petruzzi]
* Added global setting ("stripFromSQL") to only include safe characters in raw SQL - [Per Djurner]

View Enhancements
=================
* Added a better way to escape all HTML entities - [James Gibson]
* Ability to use custom types (HTML 5) on all form helpers - [Raul Riera, Per Djurner]
* Default to the humanized property name for labels on calculated or non-persistent properties instead of throwing an error - [Andy Bellenie]
* Added escapeHTML argument on simpleFormat() - [Chris Peters]
* Made it possible to set global defaults on autoLink(), excerpt(), highlight() and simpleFormat() - [Chris Peters]
* Added support for array of structs for select() and selectTag() - #680 [William Fisk, Tony Petruzzi]
* Added label and labelTag view helpers - [Tony Petruzzi] 
* Made it possible to set a global default for the "twelveHour" argument on form helpers - [Per Djurner]
* Support for implicit protocol in JavaScriptIncludeTag() and styleSheetLinkTag() - [Per Djurner]
* New form helpers radioButtonTagGroup() and checkBoxTagGroup() - [Chris Peters, Per Djurner]
* New "aroundRight" option on "labelPlacement" argument that places label text to the right of the form input - [Per Djurner]
* Added "prepend" / "append" arguments on buttonTag() and submitTag() - [Per Djurner]
* Allow to show labels without text by specifying "label=true" from "Tag" type functions - [Per Djurner]
* Support for boolean HTML5 attributes - [Per Djurner]
* Ability to remove "media" / "type" attributes when using styleSheetLinkTag() and JavaScriptIncludeTag() - [Per Djurner]
* Added global Setting ("dataAttributeDelimiter") to convert, for example, "dataDomCache" or "data_dom_cache" (the default) argument names to "data-dom-cache" attribute names - [Per Djurner]
* Add delimiter argument to the highlight() function - [Per Djurner]
* Provided an option to use the more semantically correct HTML5 "mark" tag in the highlight() function - [Per Djurner]
* Changed so that when passing in an array of structs to select(), selectTag() it uses the struct key as the option tag value and the struct value as the option tag text instead of vice versa - [Per Djurner]

Controller Enhancements
=======================
* Speed improvement for finding routes when using a large amount of named routes - [James Gibson]
* Wheels now compacts the output of the rendered content - [James Gibson]
* Added the ability to pass through arguments from the view to the Data Function in the controller - [Per Djurner]
* Changed so that cookies (when using them as storage for the Flash) are HTTPOnly and secure (when applicable) - [Per Djurner]
* Stripped line break characters from internal "cfheader" and "cfmail" usage for improved security - [Per Djurner]

Other Enhancements
==================
* Added automatic caching in production mode of function results based on the arguments passed in - [Per Djurner]
* Plugin functions can now be injected into base model adapter and model connection components - [Per Djurner]
* Added support for Unobstructive Javascript - [Raul Riera]
* Added proper HTTP status headers - #705 [cfconcepts, Andy Bellenie]
* Added favicon to URL rewrite exclusions [Troy Murray, Cathy Shapiro]
* Adds helper for utc timestamps [Andy Bellenie]
* Allow custom mailparams to by passed to sendEmail() - #85 [forday, Tony Petruzzi]
* Allow different form and to email addresses in sendEmail() - #95 [Andy Bellenie, Tony Petruzzi]
* Allow any variable type to be passed as params to urlFor() - [Tony Petruzzi]
* Pass along arguments to "onSessionEnd" so one can access the application and session scopes in the correct way inside "events/onsessionend.cfm" - [Per Djurner]
* For security reasons, only allow .cfm files with normal characters to be included - [Per Djurner]
* Improved performance by avoiding a Duplicate() call when sending error emails - [Per Djurner]
* General performance improvement for internal locking - [Per Djurner]

Bug Fixes
=========
* Allow blank values to be passed through to validation - #638 [Per Djurner]
* Allow for encoding autodetection within provides - #674 [Raul Riera]
* Transactions would not close when used with the dependent argument of hasMany() - #739 [Andy Bellenie]
* Soft deletes now work correctly with outer joins - #762 [Andy Bellenie]
* Pagination with compound keys - #725 [Andy Bellenie, jfeasel, Tony Petruzzi]
* Prevent automatic validation from being set on user defined primary keys - #778 [Mike Henke, Tony Petruzzi]
* Calculated properties were not being returned when specifying the select on findAll - #69 [kapitaine, Tony Petruzzi]
* Duplicate object ids could occur when adding nested properties - #76 [Sam Hakimi, [James Gibson, Tony Petruzzi]
* Incorrect pagination query with Oracle - #93 [crsedgar, Tony Petruzzi]
* Fixed so autoLink() does not link URLs in tag attributes when quoted - [Per Djurner]
* Removed old bug fix to make redirectTo() respect anchors - #857 [Per Djurner]
* Added work-around for "FastHashRemoved" struct bug found in ColdFusion 8 - [Per Djurner]
* Cached queries did not respect the "maxRows" argument - [Per Djurner, Tony Petruzzi]
* radioButtonTag() checked attribute was ignored if value attribute is empty - [Per Djurner]
* Fixed error when using hyphenated attributes in linkTo() - [Per Djurner]

Miscellaneous
=============
* Removed the "cacheDatabaseSchema" setting, "cacheModelInitialization" should now be used instead - [Per Djurner]
* Added commented out settig for plugin development in design mode - #782 [Tony Petruzzi]
* Added $inspect method to return the variables scope of objects - #820 [Tony Petruzzi]
* Renamed `renderPage` to `renderView` - #363 [Andy Bellenie, Tony Petruzzi]
* Case insensitive loading of controllers and models - [Per Djurner]
* Allow placement of models in subfolder - [Tim Badolato, Tony Petruzzi]
* External paths for imagePath - [andoradmiraal, Tony Petruzzi]
* Removal of obfuscateParam and deobfuscateParam functionality - [Tony Petruzzi]
* Removed the ability to switch environment through the url unless specified in config/settings.cfm - [Andy Bellenie, Tony Petruzzi]
* Turned off URL rewriting in IIS 7 by default since otherwise it will throw an error when the URL Rewrite Module is not installed - [Per Djurner]

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

